 1446:     """
 1447:     Susceptible, Exposed, Infected, Removed (SEIR)
 1448:     The infected class has 5 groups:
 1449:     * Ia: asymptomatic
 1450:     * Is: symptomatic
 1451:     * Ih: hospitalized
 1452:     * Ic: ICU
 1453:     * Im: Mortality
 1454:     S  ---> E
 1455:     E  ---> Ia, Is
 1456:     Ia ---> R
 1457:     Is ---> Ih, R
 1458:     Ih ---> Ic, R
 1459:     Ic ---> Im, R
 1460:     Parameters
 1461:     ----------
 1462:     parameters: dict
 1463:         Contains the following keys:
 1464:             alpha: float, np.array (M,)
 1465:                 fraction of infected who are asymptomatic.
 1466:             beta: float
 1467:                 rate of spread of infection.
 1468:             gE: float
 1469:                 rate of removal from exposeds individuals.
 1470:             gIa: float
 1471:                 rate of removal from asymptomatic individuals.
 1472:             gIs: float
 1473:                 rate of removal from symptomatic individuals.
 1474:             gIh: float
 1475:                 rate of removal for hospitalised individuals.
 1476:             gIc: float
 1477:                 rate of removal for idividuals in intensive care.
 1478:             fsa: float
 1479:                 fraction by which symptomatic individuals self isolate.
 1480:             fh  : float
 1481:                 fraction by which hospitalised individuals are isolated.
 1482:             sa: float, np.array (M,)
 1483:                 daily arrival of new susceptables.
 1484:                 sa is rate of additional/removal of population by birth etc
 1485:             hh: float, np.array (M,)
 1486:                 fraction hospitalised from Is
 1487:             cc: float, np.array (M,)
 1488:                 fraction sent to intensive care from hospitalised.
 1489:             mm: float, np.array (M,)
 1490:                 mortality rate in intensive care
 1491:     M: int
 1492:         Number of compartments of individual for each class.
 1493:         I.e len(contactMatrix)
 1494:     Ni: np.array(8*M, )
 1495:         Initial number in each compartment and class
 1496:     Methods
 1497:     -------
 1498:     simulate
 1499:     """
 1500:     cdef:
 1501:         double gIa, gIs, gIh, gIc, fsa, fh, gE
 1502:         np.ndarray alpha, sa, hh, cc, mm
